Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Thirtieth anniversary of Kennedy assassination, 1993
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00ylf0m
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 26 Nov 1993
Searching for a fair evaluation of John F Kennedy's life, 30 years after his assasination and how the significance of anniversaries is transformed by historical revisions.